{"title":"每天一个 vscode 小技巧","date":"2020-08-04T08:33:38.811Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 4, 2020","L":"08/04/2020","MM-DD":"08-04"},"link":"2020/08/04/每天一个vscode小技巧","tags":["vscode"],"updated":"2020-08-04T08:33:38.811Z","content":"<p>又学会了没用的知识呢…</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"一.mac终端用vscode打开文件\">一.mac终端用vscode打开文件<a title=\"#一.mac终端用vscode打开文件\" href=\"#一.mac终端用vscode打开文件\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>安装code命令<br>\nvsode中 <code>comand+shift+p</code> -&gt; 搜索 ‘code’ -&gt; 选择’shell 在Path中安装code命令’</li>\n<li>使用<br>\n命令行输入 <code>code [文件夹路径]</code></li>\n<li>大功告成🎉</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"二.mac完整卸载vscode\">二.mac完整卸载vscode<a title=\"#二.mac完整卸载vscode\" href=\"#二.mac完整卸载vscode\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>退出 VSCode 应用</li>\n<li>输入如下指令，删除 VSCode 的设置和配置</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><figcaption><span>rm -rf $HOME/Library/Application\\ Support/Code```</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">3. 输入如下指令，删除 VSCode 的插件</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#96;&#96;&#96;sudo rm -rf $HOME&#x2F;.vscode</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>从 Application 中移除 VSCode</li>\n</ol>\n","next":{"title":"啊哈！ 算法","link":"2020/08/04/啊哈算法"},"plink":"http://qiuxiaori.github.com/2020/08/04/每天一个vscode小技巧/","toc":[{"id":"一.mac终端用vscode打开文件","title":"一.mac终端用vscode打开文件","index":"1"},{"id":"二.mac完整卸载vscode","title":"二.mac完整卸载vscode","index":"2"}],"copyright":{"author":"Qiu Xiaori","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名（CC BY-NC-ND 4.0)","link":"<a href=\"http://qiuxiaori.github.com/2020/08/04/每天一个vscode小技巧/\" title=\"每天一个 vscode 小技巧\">http://qiuxiaori.github.com/2020/08/04/每天一个vscode小技巧/</a>"}}